{
  "stem": "1160.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He always looked at us with meanness.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The next thing I noticed, the wagon is moving.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The wagon is moving, and when we go out, when we start to go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You see, they broke down the fences between the properties there, so we went over to the other side of the street.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We went on the-- we didn't go out-- come out from the Jewish street, because the ghetto was there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You see, the ghetto was-- it was locked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were locked in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The beginning of the street, there was a big fence-- wooden fence-- put up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the end of the street there was a big wooden fence.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But when they were taking us already to the train, they broke down the fence that was between the property and the other side of the other street.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We went out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "As the way-- the wagon is moving, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I looked to my right, and I see my [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Safar ?] grandmother, on a summer chair, sitting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She wasn't able to walk already for years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She was put out always, you know, summertime for fresh air, but she had to be carried.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then I said to my mother again, look, grandmother is there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I feel a terrible pain, a terrible pain in my heart.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My grandmother, we are going--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she's left behind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she's there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She's there, sitting alone, and we are moving.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The pain was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother says, she will-- she will be with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then the wagon is going, and we-- [INAUDIBLE] we go through this place, where before, we had to give in all our jewelries.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
